    dcterms:description "The overall goal of the ALI research programme is to enable work toward a systematic understanding of the language situation in Iran. This initiative is guided by a set of interrelated themes which are: language distribution, linguistic and areal typology, language classification and language documentation. The output of the project can be found online in form of interactive maps and visualizations."@en ;
