    dcterms:description "This project is a first ever attempt to compile a digital trilingual and linguistically annotated parallel corpus of Greek classical scientific and philosophical literature and the Syriac and Arabic translations thereof. Besides an online lexicography the database is enhanced by a linguistic corpus management system providing advanced search tools which help to compare and analyze the texts in all three languages."@en ;
