    dcterms:description "The project seeks to organize the collaboration of numerous scholars in developing an electronic text collection. This collection will serve as a foundation for computer-aided investigations into diverse Indo-European languages. Additionally, the project aims to expand the initiative by generating a growing repository of files containing supplementary materials, including dictionaries, word lists, linguistic analysis tools, and similar resources."@en ;
