    dcterms:description "Main goal of the project was to create the first machine-actionable premodern Persian corpus. Currently the project is focused on two inter-linked projects: (1) the construction of a scholarly-verified and machine actionable corpus, and (2) the development of optical character recognition (OCR)/handwritten text recognition (HTR) tools for Persian (and other Arabic-script languages)."@en ;
