    dcterms:description "CLARIN-D is a research-oriented infrastructure for the Humanities and Social Sciences which supports researchers with accessing, preparing and analyzing of research data based on all language-related resources. It offers information on a wide range of topics, including teaching material, help on data management plans and other, discipline-specific support and makes available tools for Humanities, Cultural and Social Sciences scholars to analyze their research data in different ways. It is a German center of a pan-European research infrastructure CLARIN."@en ;
