    dcterms:description "The purpose if this project was to edit documents from the MA thesis “Die Schreiben Selims II. aus dem Haus-, Hof- und Staatsarchiv zu Wien und die habsburgisch-osmanischen Beziehungen zwischen 1566 und 1574,” Vienna 2020, written by Halit Temiz and supervised by Univ.-Prof. Dr. Claudia Römer. They were converted into TEI-XML within the framework of the project Digital Edition of Sources on Habsburg-Ottoman Diplomacy 1500-1918 (QhoD), including all apparatus, and are available here under free license as an XML corpus."@en ;
