    dcterms:description "The aim of the project is preparation of a diachronic corpus of Egyptian texts which, linked to a digital dictionary, enables online research of Coptic vocabulary throughout all epochs and stages of Egyptian language history. The results are accessible on Thesaurus Linguae Aegyptiae (TLA), a research and publishing platform developed by a previous BBAW project, “Altägyptisches Wörterbuch,” which expired 2012."@en ;
    dcterms:identifier "85d053c3-4ce6-4130-bc6a-63f96acfb067" ;
