    dcterms:created "2021-11-08"^^xsd:date ;
    dcterms:description "The project’s main goal is to generate a trilingual critical edition of all commentaries by Ibn Rušd (Averroes) on Aristotle’s Physics, which are the synthesis of the late antique and Arabic reception of Greek philosophy. Next to the Arabic commentaries the edition will also contain their Latin and Hebrew translations."@en ;
