    dcterms:description "SfarData is a bilingual (Hebrew/English) codicological database of the dated medieval manuscripts written in Hebrew script documented in 250 libraries. It has a 50 years long history of digital preservation of bibliographical, textual, numerical, and paleographical data and was recently incorporated to the National Library of Israel."@en ;
