    dcterms:description "This project is intended to support the research program of the SFB (Sonderforschungsbereich for Manuscript Cultures in Asia, Africa and Europe) by piloting and further development of the Advanced Manuscript Analysis Portal (AMAP), a web-based platform offering self-usable toolbox for humanists and facilitating communication between experts, as well as by development of innovative image processing methods."@en ;
